TATTOO: Atlantean magical tattoos

Syntax: tattoo
        tattoo list
        tattoo activate <number|name|location>
        tattoo status
        tattoo help

DESCRIPTION:
  Manage and activate magical tattoos. Available to Atlanteans, Sunaj
  Assassins, Tattooed Men, and characters with the tattoo_capable property.

  tattoo list
      Show all tattoos with list numbers and body locations.

  tattoo activate <number|name|location>
      Activate one tattoo by list number, display name, or body location.

  tattoo status
      Show active timed tattoos and time remaining.

  tattoo help
      Extended in-command help.

NOTES:
  Weapon tattoos summon magical weapons. Armor tattoos create force fields.
  Power tattoos have varied effects. Passive tattoos stay active.
  Duplicate activation of an active timed tattoo is blocked.
  New tattoos are inscribed by Tattoo Master NPCs in Atlantean cities.

SEE ALSO: psionics, score, abilities
